==English and Irish==

===Etymology===
The title translates into "The Book of the Taking of Ireland"

===Proper Noun===
{{Wikipedia}}
'''Lebor Gabála Érenn'''

#''Irish texts''. The [[Middle Irish]] title of a loose collection of [[poem]]s and [[prose]] [[narrative]]s recounting the mythical origins and history of an Irish race from the creation of the world down to the [[Middle Ages]].